--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Item_unit_pattern_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 125e99b9e75c73a48879818b46a63f99, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 99025915904
    m_Localized: 'Upgrade 1 '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 99084636160
    m_Localized: Upgrade 2
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 99084636161
    m_Localized: Upgrade 3
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 99084636162
    m_Localized: Default pattern
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 99088830464
    m_Localized: Passive pattern
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 99088830465
    m_Localized: Active pattern
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043184492544
    m_Localized: Musket firing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212800
    m_Localized: Marine fires one bullet forward. The bullet causes 100% of the damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212801
    m_Localized: Musket triple shoot
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212802
    m_Localized: Marine fires 3 bullets forward. The bullets cause 60% damage. This
      pattern is used as a substitute for the default pattern.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212803
    m_Localized: Musket penta shoot
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212804
    m_Localized: Marine fires 5 bullets forward. The bullets cause 50% damage. This
      pattern is used as a substitute for the default pattern.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212805
    m_Localized: Carrot throw
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212806
    m_Localized: 'Pekora throws a carrot to the damaged unit to restore HP (Recovery
      amount: Pekora''s POWER 100%).'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043243212807
    m_Localized: New food Added!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407104
    m_Localized: 'Pekora adds two new foods besides carrots.

      - almond : In
      addition to the carrot''s recovery effect, increase the unit''s POWER by 30%
      for 4 seconds.

      - Cold chicken : In addition to the carrot''s recovery
      effect, it increases the unit''s attack speed by 30% for 4 seconds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407105
    m_Localized: Big Carrot Explosion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407106
    m_Localized: 'Pekora casts a Big Carrot Explosion on the unit at the forefront.
      The Big Carrot Explosion deals 400% damage to monsters within the area, while
      increasing all units'' POWER by 40%, attack speed by 40%, and maximum HP by
      40% for 7 seconds (Cooldown: 30 seconds).'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407107
    m_Localized: Fireball
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407108
    m_Localized: Flare fires a fireball forward. The fireball deals 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407109
    m_Localized: Hellfire
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407110
    m_Localized: Every 4th attack, Flare casts Hellfire on the enemy with the highest
      health. Hellfire deals 250% damage to all monsters within its range.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407111
    m_Localized: Fire breath
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407112
    m_Localized: Flare casts Fire breath in front of her, dealing 600% damage divided
      over 20 hits to all monsters within its range. Each time the Fire breath hits,
      Hellfire will be cast automatically with 5% chance (cooltime 18 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407113
    m_Localized: Mace attack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407114
    m_Localized: Noel whips Mace and causes 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407115
    m_Localized: Enormous power
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407116
    m_Localized: For every fourth attack, Noel whips Mace three times, dealing 360%
      of the damage. The last attack stuns the monster for two seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407117
    m_Localized: Shout of a Knight
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407118
    m_Localized: Noel shouts loudly. It causes 150% damage to monsters within range
      and pulls them in front of Noel  (cooltime 8 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407119
    m_Localized: Trident stabbing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407120
    m_Localized: Gura stabs the monster with a trident, causing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407121
    m_Localized: Sea explosion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407122
    m_Localized: Every second attack, Gura causes a sea explosion. It causes 100%
      additional damage to monsters in range.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407123
    m_Localized: Waterfall
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407124
    m_Localized: Every second attack, Gura creates a wave, causing 150% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407125
    m_Localized: JabJabStraight
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407126
    m_Localized: Korone attacks 3 times. The first 2 attacks cause 100% damage, 200%
      damage at last.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407127
    m_Localized: Jab rush
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407128
    m_Localized: Korone throws a flurry of jabs every 4.5 seconds, dealing 450% damage
      split among the targets. This ability is executed even while other patterns
      are in progress.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407129
    m_Localized: DOOG PUNCH
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407130
    m_Localized: Every time Korone causes damage to a monster, she uses DOOG PUNCH
      with a 30% chance to cause an additional 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407131
    m_Localized: Harp play
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407132
    m_Localized: Watame plays the harp to create a melody. The melody causes 100%
      damage to up to five monsters and slows them down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407133
    m_Localized: Exciting melody
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407134
    m_Localized: Watame plays the harp in a creative way to create melody area. On
      melody area, Units' attack speed increases by 30%, and monsters' movespeed
      decreases (cooltime 12 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407135
    m_Localized: Yo-yo strike
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407136
    m_Localized: Subaru throws a yo-yo, causing 200% damage to the monster over 2
      times. The first attack pushes the monster.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407137
    m_Localized: Subaduck rush
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407138
    m_Localized: A Subaduck appears and races forward. Subaduck pushes the monster
      away and causes 150% damage (cooltime 7 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407139
    m_Localized: Jet-engine yo-yo
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407140
    m_Localized: The push force of the yo-yo is increased by 1.5 times (this does
      not affect the push force of Subaduck). The damage of the yo-yo's second hit
      is increased by 50%.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407141
    m_Localized: Revolver firing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407142
    m_Localized: Watson fires the detective's revolver, causing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407143
    m_Localized: Machine-gun firing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407144
    m_Localized: For every third attack, watson fires a machine gun and causes 450%
      damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407145
    m_Localized: Time acceleration
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8043247407146
    m_Localized: Watson accelerates time with her special watch, speeding up the
      attackspeed by 40% for 15 seconds. If there is a unit that died on a pattern
      trial, selects an random respawn point and halves the death waiting time (cooltime
      20 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470138601472
    m_Localized: Scythe swinging
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470188933120
    m_Localized: Calliope whips a sickle and causes 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470197321728
    m_Localized: Soul harvest
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470197321729
    m_Localized: "When Calliope is on the field, there is a 5% chance to obtain a
      soul when a monster dies. Each time a certain number of souls are collected,
      Calliope's POWER permanently increases during that game (4 POWER per 10 souls).
      \nDefeating a boss guarantees obtaining an enhanced soul, which grants a stack
      equivalent to 50 regular souls."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470197321730
    m_Localized: Death-sensei escort
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470197321731
    m_Localized: Every 4th attack, Calliope summons "Death Sensei." Death Sensei
      initially pushes enemies back and then fires a "Death Slash" projectile in
      front, dealing 200% damage before disappearing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470197321732
    m_Localized: Death coil
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3405470197321733
    m_Localized: Calliope fires 'Death Coil' in 8 directions. Each causes 100% Damage
      (cooltime 12 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3636951524020224
    m_Localized: Play with Sheep
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3636951578546176
    m_Localized: At the start of the game, Watame summons the sheep. It has a lot
      of HP instead of having no pattern to use and unable to restore its HP.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10938678543618048
    m_Localized: Angel Bat
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10938678589755392
    m_Localized: Kanata swings the bat, dealing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10938678589755393
    m_Localized: Angel Ring Shuriken
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10938678589755394
    m_Localized: For every 6.5 seconds, Kanata summons 3 Angel Ring Shurikens. When
      Kanata uses her next pattern while Angel Ring Shurikens are summoned, the shurikens
      fly out, dealing 240% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10938678589755395
    m_Localized: Fastball at 500km/h
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10938678589755396
    m_Localized: Kanata gains 1 "Angel Count" with each attack. When casting a pattern,
      all accumulated Angel Counts are consumed, dealing damage equal to (consumed
      Angel Counts x 6 + 200%) (cooldown 15 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23204322928463872
    m_Localized: Dessert time!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23204322974601216
    m_Localized: 'Luna summons desserts on random tiles in the back 3 rows. When
      a unit picks up a dessert, they receive various buffs depending on the type
      of dessert.

      - Macaron: Provides a healing effect(100% of Luna''s POWER)
      and increases the unit''s POWER by 50% for 5 seconds.

      - Chocolate: Provides
      a healing effect(100% of Luna''s POWER) and increases the unit''s attackSpeed
      by 50% for 5 seconds.

      - Gingerbread Man: Provides a healing effect(100%
      of Luna''s POWER) and increases the unit''s HP by 50% for 5 seconds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23204322974601217
    m_Localized: Help me, lu-knight!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23204322974601218
    m_Localized: Lu-knight responds to Luna's call and flies in to protect her. Lu-knight
      deals 50% damage to the first monster it collides with, then lands behind that
      monster. Afterward, it deals 60% damage twice, and with its final attack, it
      deals 60% damage in a 3x3 area, stunning the monsters and then disappearing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23204322974601219
    m_Localized: Luna Time
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23204322974601220
    m_Localized: 'Luna can summon a "Magic Candy" as her 10th dessert. The effects
      of the Magic Candy change depending on which unit acquires it.

      If a
      unit other than Luna acquires it: Increases the POWER, attack speed, and HP
      of all units except Luna by 50% for 7 seconds.

      If Luna acquires it:
      Luna enters "Luna Time" along with the above buff effects. During Luna Time,
      Lu-knight is summoned on 10 random tiles, and the default pattern is replaced
      with "Help me, lu-knight!" for the duration.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040371900416
    m_Localized: Fubuki performs a scratch attack to the front, dealing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649152
    m_Localized: Fox Scratch
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649153
    m_Localized: 'Fubuki draws her katana and unleashes a blade storm to the front,
      dealing 150% damage. When this pattern is used, Fubuki recovers 2% of the Dark
      Gauge.


      (While in Kurokami transformation) unleashes two blade storms
      to the front, each dealing 150% damage. The Dark Gauge is not recovered.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649154
    m_Localized: Katana Wind
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649155
    m_Localized: (Available during Kurokami transformation) Kurokami performs a series
      of scratch attacks, dealing a total of 280% damage. Fubuki recovers 1/3 of
      the damage dealt as HP.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649156
    m_Localized: Frenzied Scratch
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649157
    m_Localized: 'Fubuki uses the Dark Gauge. Fubuki automatically recovers the gauge
      over time, and while the Dark Gauge is active, she can transform into Kurokami
      Fubuki. During the transformation, attack speed increases by 50%.


      While
      transformed into Kurokami, the gauge gradually decreases. When the gauge reaches
      zero, she instantly reverts to Shirakami and enters a dormant state for 15
      seconds. During the dormant state, she cannot transform into Kurokami, but
      after the dormant state ends, the gauge recovers by 30%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33428040409649158
    m_Localized: Kurokami Fubuki
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41341107852251136
    m_Localized: Laser Rifle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41341107902582784
    m_Localized: Towa fires laser rifle forward, causing 100% damage to up to 3 monsters.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41341107906777088
    m_Localized: Devil's Kiss
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41341107906777089
    m_Localized: 'For every 4th attack, Towa shoots a powerful laser forward, causing
      200% damage to enemy monsters, and restoring the HP of ally units (Recovery
      amount: Towa''s POWER 50%).'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41341107906777090
    m_Localized: Attraction of Fascination
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41341107906777091
    m_Localized: Towa throws a grenade in front. The grenade creates a 'black hole'
      object at the point where it first hits the monster. The black hole continuously
      attracts monsters within the 3X3 range, causing a total of 300% damage (cooldown
      18 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346188460032
    m_Localized: Ancient Feather
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403072
    m_Localized: Mumei fires a single 'feather projectile' imbued with special power,
      dealing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403073
    m_Localized: Feather Explosion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403074
    m_Localized: Each time the feather projectile hits a monster, one feather gets
      stuck in the monster. When 3 feathers are stuck, it triggers an explosion,
      dealing 150% damage to the enemy and removing all stuck feathers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403075
    m_Localized: Power of Bonds
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403076
    m_Localized: Mumei awakens the power of her friends, enhancing her default pattern.
      For 10 seconds, her attack speed is increased by 30%, and the number of feather
      projectiles she can fire is increased to 3 (cooldown 15 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403077
    m_Localized: Feather FLOWER
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43790346230403078
    m_Localized: The damage of Feather Explosion is increased to 250%. Each time
      a Feather Explosion occurs, 5 'piercing feather projectiles' are additionally
      fired behind the monster. The piercing feather projectiles deal 50% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155280793600
    m_Localized: Flower in a snow
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125248
    m_Localized: Lamy continuously summons a blizzard, dealing 20% damage to monsters
      within a 3x3 area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125249
    m_Localized: Frost Explosion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125250
    m_Localized: Lamy causes a frost explosion, dealing 100% damage to monsters within
      a 3x3 area. When on a fire floor, it changes to a flame explosion, dealing
      200% damage to monsters within a 5x5 area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125251
    m_Localized: Bottle of Sake
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125252
    m_Localized: Every 20 seconds, Lamy drinks sake to forget the cold and changes
      the blizzard to a fire floor. The fire floor deals 40% damage to monsters within
      a 5x5 area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125253
    m_Localized: Snowstorm
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49851155331125254
    m_Localized: Lamy surrounds herself with ice, becoming immune to damage for 6
      seconds, and summons a blizzard that deals a total of 900% damage to all monsters
      on the map (cooldown 35 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118219554816
    m_Localized: Melody
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886464
    m_Localized: Suisei sings a song to unleash a sonic attack, dealing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886465
    m_Localized: Sui-chopath
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886466
    m_Localized: Suisei throws a golden axe, dealing 150% damage. The golden axe
      projectile bounces whenever it hits the edge of the map and persists for 7
      seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886467
    m_Localized: piece of the star
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886468
    m_Localized: Suisei summons star fragments from the sky, dealing 300% damage.
      If a monster is defeated by this pattern, a Stardust stack is earned. Once
      50 Stardust stacks are collected, the pattern changes to the 'Comet' pattern
      (cooldown 12 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886469
    m_Localized: Comet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52469118269886470
    m_Localized: Suisei summons a comet onto the field, dealing 600% damage to all
      monsters and stunning them for 5 seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857250349056
    m_Localized: Tree of Life
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292096
    m_Localized: 'Fauna grows the Tree of Life, which can grow up to 3 stages. At
      stage 3, if the default pattern is used again, a "Wind of Life" blows, healing
      allied units within a 5x5 range. Afterward, the tree disappears, and on the
      next use of the default pattern, it begins growing again from stage 1. (Healing
      Amount: 100% of Fauna''s POWER).'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292097
    m_Localized: Sowing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292098
    m_Localized: Each time "Wind of Life" activates, all units receiving the healing
      effect are targeted with Sowing. Units that have been sown can grow plants
      alongside Fauna and receive different seeds depending on their role type. The
      plants grow in tandem with Fauna's Tree of Life, reaching up to 3 stages. At
      stage 3, they provide a buff effect to units within a 3x3 range. Fauna herself
      does not receive the buff effect.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292099
    m_Localized: Rapid Growth
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292100
    m_Localized: Fauna creates a tree wall in front of her for 4 seconds, blocking
      the advance of monsters. While the tree wall is up, the attack speed of Fauna
      and all units increases by 80%. (Cooldown 20 seconds).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292101
    m_Localized: Zombie Slash
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292102
    m_Localized: Ollie performs a slashing attack forward, dealing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292103
    m_Localized: Relentless Vitality
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292104
    m_Localized: Each time Ollie deals damage, she recovers 5% of that damage as
      HP. However, Ollie cannot regenerate HP on her own.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292105
    m_Localized: Zomrade
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292106
    m_Localized: For every 4th attack, Ollie summons a Zomrade at her position. Zomrade
      grows larger each time it takes a certain amount of damage and, once fully
      grown, explodes after 1 second, dealing 200% damage. If not triggered by damage,
      Zomrade will automatically explode 7 seconds after summoning.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292107
    m_Localized: Tombstone
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63813857292292108
    m_Localized: "Ollie summons a Tombstone at her position. Every 10 seconds, a
      Doll Zombie (UDIN) is summoned from the Tombstone to fight enemy monsters.
      There is a 20% chance for a strengthened Tombstone to appear, which summons
      a giant Doll Zombie with enhanced stats. The HP and POWER of Doll Zombies scale
      with Ollie\u2019s HP and POWER. Tombstone lasts for 240 seconds, and if Ollie
      retires, all summoned Tombstones disappear (Cooldown 22 seconds)."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65318533254844416
    m_Localized: Water Gun
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65318533292593152
    m_Localized: Kobo fires a water bomb using her umbrella. The water bomb deals
      100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65318533292593153
    m_Localized: Ebb Tide
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65318533292593154
    m_Localized: If the water bomb projectile goes off-screen, it transforms into
      a water wave projectile and returns to Kobo. The water wave projectile deals
      200% damage and slows monsters by 30% for 3 seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65318533296787456
    m_Localized: Rain Shaman
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65318533296787457
    m_Localized: "Kobo summons a rain cloud that lasts for 10 seconds. The rain cloud
      deals 15% damage to monsters every 0.3 seconds, and its position can be controlled
      with the mouse. \nClicking the mouse causes the rain cloud to strike lightning,
      dealing 250% damage to monsters within range and stunning them for 2 seconds.
      Lightning can be used up to 3 times, and the rain cloud disappears immediately
      after all lightning strikes are used (Cooldown 27 seconds)."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320259518464
    m_Localized: Partner Designation
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655808
    m_Localized: Sora designates the unit in front of her as a partner. If a partner
      has already been designated, the new unit in front will replace the previous
      partner, and the former partner effect will be removed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655809
    m_Localized: Partner
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655810
    m_Localized: 'Sora can designate a partner with her default pattern. The designated
      partner recovers HP and gains a 50% attack speed boost for 7 seconds whenever
      Sora uses her ''Partner Designation'' pattern. (Healing amount: 100% of POWER)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655811
    m_Localized: Star Bubble
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655812
    m_Localized: When the partner deals damage, a 'Star Bubble' projectile is fired
      forward. The 'Star Bubble' projectile deals 20% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655813
    m_Localized: Idol On Stage
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655814
    m_Localized: 'Sora creates four platforms sequentially. If Sora successfully
      steps on all platforms, all units except Sora are designated as partners for
      12 seconds. Additionally, during the duration, the partner buff effects are
      enhanced. (Cooldown: 45 seconds)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655815
    m_Localized: Sakura Flame
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655816
    m_Localized: Miko fires a Sakura Flame projectile forward, dealing 100% damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655817
    m_Localized: Fortune Paper
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655818
    m_Localized: 'Miko selects a Fortune Paper every 10 seconds. The Fortune Paper
      is either a Lucky Paper or an Unlucky Paper, with different effects based on
      the type selected. (Chance for Lucky Paper: 50%, Unlucky Paper: 50%)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655819
    m_Localized: Lucky Paper
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655820
    m_Localized: 'The Lucky Paper is summoned to a random unit, forming a 3x3 area.
      The area lasts for 3 seconds, healing units within and increasing their HP
      by 20%. (Healing amount: 20% of POWER)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655821
    m_Localized: Unlucky Paper
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655822
    m_Localized: 'The Unlucky Paper is summoned to a random monster, casting random
      misfortunes in a 3x3 area.

      - Misfortune_Magma: Summons magma, burning
      monsters within the area for 3 seconds and dealing a total of 450% damage.

      -
      Misfortune_Lightning: Strikes lightning, dealing 500% damage to monsters within
      the area and stunning them for 2 seconds.

      - Misfortune_Genloss: Instantly
      kills 3 monsters within the area. Boss monsters are excluded.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655823
    m_Localized: Sakura Path
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 85394320305655824
    m_Localized: Whenever a Fortune Paper disappears, it creates a Sakura Path in
      that lane for 3 seconds. Units stepping on the Sakura Path gain 30% POWER and
      attack speed, while monsters are slowly pushed back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
